name: SOLIPS (person... toothbrush... tie...)
description:
An original Gory Orgy animated loop. 10 seconds. 1228X1228, H264, 2021
Solips is a multi-layered animation that utilises more than one machine-learning model. A fleshy, shape-shifting figure (computer generated erotica) is conspicuously analysed by a machine-learning model that identifies people and objects. Solips (person toothbrush tie) is one of a pair. One copy is retained by the artist, while the other is available for purchase. Gory Orgy is the experimental machine-learning project by kiwi artist and film-maker Ed Lust.
